    <stitle>7 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS FULLER SERIES - DISASSEMBLE - MAINSHAFT</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="IDcomponent" graphiccount="13">
        <title>MAINSHAFT</title>
        <para>Refer to
            <hotlnk xrefid="f1302558">Figure 58</hotlnk>.
        </para>
        <figure id="f1302558" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1302558" filename="../figg13/g1302558.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 58. Mainshaft Exploded View</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove 2nd speed gear from the rear of the mainshaft and place the mainshaft assembly in a
                vise, pilot end up (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302559">Figure 59</hotlnk>). Use brass jaws or wood blocks in the vise to protect the
                mainshaft.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f1302559" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1302559" filename="../figg13/g1302559.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 59. Place Mainshaft Assembly in Vise</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove 6th and 7th speed clutch from the mainshaft (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302560">Figure 60</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f1302560" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1302560" filename="../figg13/g1302560.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 60. Remove 6th and 7th Speed Clutch From Mainshaft</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove short key (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302561">Figure 61</hotlnk>) and rotate the tolerance washer with a screwdriver to
                align the splines with those of the mainshaft (inset).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f1302561" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1302561" filename="../figg13/g1302561.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 61. Remove Short Key</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove 6th speed gear, tolerance washer and spacer from the mainshaft (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302562">Figure 62</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f1302562" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1302562" filename="../figg13/g1302562.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 62. Remove 6th Speed Gear, Tolerance Washer and Spacer</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove 5th speed gear and spacer from the mainshaft (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302563">Figure 63</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f1302563" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1302563" filename="../figg13/g1302563.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 63. Remove 5th Speed Gear and Spacer</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove 4th and 5th speed clutch from the mainshaft (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302564">Figure 64</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f1302564" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1302564" filename="../figg13/g1302564.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 64. Remove 4th and 5th Speed Clutch</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the mainshaft assembly from the vise. Re-install the mainshaft in the vise with the
                pilot of the mainshaft facing down (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302565">Figure 65</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f1302565" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1302565" filename="../figg13/g1302565.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 65. Re-Install Mainshaft in Vise</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the key from the rear of the mainshaft, rotate tolerance washer and remove the washer
                (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302566">Figure 66</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f1302566" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1302566" filename="../figg13/g1302566.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 66. Remove Key From Rear of Mainshaft</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove 2nd and 3rd speed clutch from the rear of the mainshaft (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302567">Figure 67</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f1302567" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1302567" filename="../figg13/g1302567.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 67. Remove 2nd and 3rd Speed Clutch</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Rotate 3rd speed gear tolerance washer with a small screwdriver (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302568">inset, Figure 68</hotlnk>) and remove the gear, spacer, and tolerance washer.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f1302568" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1302568" filename="../figg13/g1302568.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 68. Rotate 3rd Speed Gear Tolerance Washer</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove 4th speed gear and spacer from the mainshaft (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302569">Figure 69</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f1302569" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1302569" filename="../figg13/g1302569.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 69. Remove 4th Speed Gear and Spacer</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Rotate the tolerance washer and remove from the mainshaft (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302570">Figure 70</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f1302570" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1302570" filename="../figg13/g1302570.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 70. Rotate Tolerance Washer and Remove</caption>
        </figure>
    </svcproc>
